entation\n\n## OpenSpec Detection\n\nThe code checks for OpenSpec installation by:\n- Running `cmdExists(DEPS.openspec.cliCmd)` to verify the CLI command exists\n- Executing `\"openspec --version\"` to retrieve the installed version\n- Storing both the installation status and version string in the response\n\n## Superpowers Detection\nâĶ","sessionId":"8465e0ee-aa91-493c-bd46-738b7cc848b5","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01RqtjM5Uv3ZUYpz5pxMExnV\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-07T17:37:53.493Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkh0w_492d95c9a736":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkh0w_492d95c9a736","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01YQxrrooM53SksDsQEPwPCh\"} | # Skills Generation & Deployment Overview\n\n## Generation Flow\n\nThe `generateSkills()` function orchestrates skill creation across specified tools:\n\n1. **Directory Resolution**: Skills deploy to `<baseDir>/<toolPaths.skillsDir>/openflow/`\n   - Global mode: `~/.config/` or equivalent home directory\n   - Local mode: Current working directory\n\n2. **FilâĶ","sessionId":"8465e0ee-aa91-493c-bd46-738b7cc848b5","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01YQxrrooM53SksDsQEPwPCh\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-07T17:37:54.745Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkh0w_d7ff175e2212":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkh0w_d7ff175e2212","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"8465e0ee-aa91-493c-bd46-738b7cc848b5","timestamp":"2026-06-07T17:37:57.136Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkh0w_2ce2a7148838":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkh0w_2ce2a7148838","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"url\":\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lininn/openflow/main/src/core/constants.ts\",\"prompt\":\"Return the full source verbatim. I need the exact values of DEPS (openspec, superpowers: cliCmd, npmPkg, checkPath, installHint) and TOOL_PATHS (for claude, codex, cursor, opencode: skillsDir, supe